        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Rhag`Mozdezh will drop 4 spells, and 2 items.</P><P>Funeral Pyre drops as an item, not as one of the 4 spells.  That's why it's only from this NPC.</P><P>As far as I can tell, every caster class got 2 level 60 Luclin spells - one that can drop from any of the Luclin spell droppers (Group Aego, Koadic's) and one spell that's off a particular mob (THO for wizards, Rhag 2 for necro.)</P><P>-Arbaon, Warlock, Luclin Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
